									</span><span class="accordion-header__icon p-0"><img class="accordion-header__icon__down" alt="Pfeil" src="/typo3conf/ext/rlp_base/Resources/Public/Icons/arrow_down_bold_red.svg" width="14" height="10" /><img class="accordion-header__icon__up" alt="Pfeil" src="/typo3conf/ext/rlp_base/Resources/Public/Icons/arrow_up_bold_red.svg" width="14" height="10" /></span></button></h2><div id="collapse38958" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="heading38958" data-bs-parent="#accordion-c38953"><div class="accordion-body p-0 m-0"><div id="c38958" class="container-inner py-0 my-0 frame frame-default frame-type-textmedia frame-layout-0"><div class="ce-textpic"><div class="ce-bodytext"><p><a href="https://bildung.rlp.de/eltern/" title="Eltern" target="_blank">Informationen für Eltern</a></p></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="accordion-item shadow-none rounded-0 border border-0 border-bottom-10"><h2 class="accordion-header" id="heading38965"><button class="accordion-button bg-transparent shadow-none rounded-0 border-0 p-0 py-6 m-0 collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapse38965" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapse38965"><span class="accordion-header__text h3 m-0 p-0 pe-2">
										
